{"tid":2016091,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"G.E.M.被爆1月已秘婚 男女家成員IG見同場","createTime":"2020-05-14T06:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T07:39:15.000Z","uid":252078,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9d28ef0607ffac33face4d71a287c1dd69c9f4","tid":2016091,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsaTYMt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsaTYMt.jpg&h=538e9535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從3年前被拍到和富二代造型師魏俊杰(Mark)，拖手行街，鄧紫棋(G.E.M.)和Mark的戀情便曝光。而且今日傳媒爆出消息，指收到爆料，說28歲的G.E.M.其實早於今年1月25日大年初一已經在泰國舉行了一場婚禮。而翻看IG，又的確看到男女家都有家人當日同時現身擬似一個外國酒店泳池池畔。<br />\n<br />\n據說當日只是一場小型婚禮，只有雙方部份家人及密友出席。而翻看G.E.M.的IG，當日他上載了一張和外公的合照，背景是一個泳池，幾日後亦有上載和妹妹在同一個泳池的合照。之後男方的妹妹在1月26日亦有上載一張照片，背景又是同一個泳池。不過Mark在回應傳媒時就否認已經結婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDoKkZV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDoKkZV.jpg&h=d2690d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我淨係想問佢阿妹個樣做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pF8RLrN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpF8RLrN.jpg&h=f68ab156&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62e12e2ede88360581e3ede3cd347d3f8c4fb5c9","tid":2016091,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"個妹P圖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb28b2f308a4ed9a561a6cd2042c80ba39f2d3eb","tid":2016091,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:54:38.000Z","msg":"魏俊杰"},{"pid":"65a39500d279cd164cd7f01a38fa5cfe4aec